    Auction

    Audience

    Bid
    Class to manage bids A bid comprises: an item or lot being bid for a bidder an amount being bid or offered for the lot
    Catalogue
    Class that contains and manages catalogue of auction lots
    Lot
    Class to create and manage an auction lot
